NK041(di)006:0: smin gling mchod rten thig tshad rab gsal me long zhes bya bar /
NK041(di)006:1: mchod rten thig tshad mdor bsdus la /
NK041(di)006:2: byang chub chen po'i mchod rten ni //
NK041(di)006:3: yar mar cha chen bcu bdun la //
NK041(di)006:4: cha phran gcig bsnan phan tshun srid //
NK041(di)006:5: cha chen bcu yin re re'i zheng //
NK041(di)006:6: cha phran bzhi bzhir bgo bar bya //
NK041(di)006:7: sa 'dzin dpang la cha phran bzhi //
NK041(di)006:8: srid du tshangs nas g.yas g.yon du //
NK041(di)006:9: cha phran bco brgyad dam phyed bcu dgu //
NK041(di)006:10: them skas rim gsum dpang cha re //
NK041(di)006:11: srid du bcu bdun bcu drug lnga //
NK041(di)006:12: khri dpang drug la srid bcu bzhi //
NK041(di)006:13: pad chung gnyis la dpang cha re //
NK041(di)006:14: srid du bco lnga bcu drug re //
NK041(di)006:15: pad chen dpang gsum srid bcu bdun //
NK041(di)006:16: rmang rten dpang gcig srid bcu drug /
NK041(di)006:17: tshad med bzhi la dpang gnyis re //
NK041(di)006:18: srid du bcu gnyis bcu gsum dang //
NK041(di)006:19: bcu gnyis bcu gcig mas rim bzhin //
NK041(di)006:20: tshad med bzhi po mdzes bya'i phyir //
NK041(di)006:21: kha pad byas na cha phran gcig /
NK041(di)006:22: sum char bsgos pa 'bur stabs bya //
NK041(di)006:23: 'phyar tshad kyang de tsam byas pas 'grub //
NK041(di)006:24: mgur chu dpang gcig srid bcu pad //
NK041(di)006:25: bum dpang bcu bzhi rtsa rtse'i srid //
NK041(di)006:26: dgu yin bcu gcig nas ni phyir //
NK041(di)006:27: cha gsum gyen la thig rtse sbrel //
NK041(di)006:28: bre gdan dpang gcig srid du bzhi //
NK041(di)006:29: bre mgul dpang gnyis srid phyed gsum //
NK041(di)006:30: gzungs sa gnyis po dpang phyed re //
NK041(di)006:31: srid du gsum dang phyed bzhi re //
NK041(di)006:32: bre dngos dpang gnyis srid bzhi'o //
NK041(di)006:34: srid du rtsa gsum rtse bzhi pad //
NK041(di)006:35: chos 'khor bcu gsum dpang bcu gsum //
NK041(di)006:36: srid du rtse gcig rtsa ba bzhi //
NK041(di)006:37: cha re'i sum gnyis pho 'khor dang //
NK041(di)006:38: sum gcig mo 'khor rtags kyang mtshungs //
NK041(di)006:39: thugs rje mdo gzungs pad+ma'i dbyibs //
NK041(di)006:40: rtsa dpang cha gcig rtse phyed gnyis //
NK041(di)006:41: gzhu bsnol dpang gcig srid phyed gsum //
NK041(di)006:42: gdugs dpang cha gcig srid du gsum //
NK041(di)006:43: de mthar zar tshags dpang gsum la //
NK041(di)006:44: mtha' rgya cha bzhi g.yel kha bya //
NK041(di)006:45: zla ba cha gcig nyi ma gnyis //
NK041(di)006:46: de steng tog la cha phran gcig /
NK041(di)006:47: cung zad mdzes par bya dgos so ////
NK041(di)006:48: rten la nang gzungs 'bul tshul 'thor bu ni /
NK041(di)006:49: srog shing ring thung mchod rten gyi gdong chen nas chos 'khor bar sleb pa /
NK041(di)006:50: lugs gcig la bum gdan nas bre yan chad zlum po'ang chog nyi zla'i bar btang ba dang /
NK041(di)006:51: lha la skyil krung nas gtsug tor bar dang /
NK041(di)006:52: lugs gcig la lte 'og nas spyi bo'i bar gsungs /
NK041(di)006:53: de la mchod rten dang rdo rje ma brkos kyang chad skyon med /
NK041(di)006:54: brko na rnam rgyal mchod rten bang rim zlum po
NK041(di)006:55: gsum can la seng khri yod lugs med lugs gnyis
NK041(di)006:56: gang byed chog / rdo rje'i rwa ngos la 'phrod
NK041(di)006:57: par bya zhing rwa 'og tu 'phang lo'ang rang dod
NK041(di)006:59: mi brko na rtsa ba'i sta bzhi cung zad re bzhog /
NK041(di)006:60: rtse mo'i ngos bzhi nas cung zad re rtser gzhol bar bzhog nas /
NK041(di)006:63: nub tu h+r+aih byang du +aah steng du /
NK041(di)006:69: nub h+r+aih byang +aah gzungs khung rnams su dri bzang dang sman 'dam byug nas /
NK041(di)006:70: spyi bo'i khung bur mchod rten la rnam rgyal ma'i gzungs dang /
NK041(di)006:71: 'od zer dri med gzungs mdo tshang ma /
NK041(di)006:72: ma shong na nye spar rtse mo zhes pa tshar grangs gar 'byor chog /
NK041(di)006:75: lte ba'i khung bu bzhi la srog shing sngags dang
NK041(di)006:76: sgrib sel gzungs gnyis tshar 99 re 'jug dgos pas
NK041(di)006:77: phyogs gsum la 25re phyogs gcig la 24phul /
NK041(di)006:78: rtsa ba'i khung bur 'od dri'i snying po dang rten snying mang nyung ci 'byor phul /
NK041(di)006:79: srog shing tsan+dana dmar po yin na tshon byug mi dgos dri bzang byug /
NK041(di)006:80: gzhan la tshon dmar po sogs skabs dang mthun par te /
NK041(di)006:81: dbang po lag pa'am 'o ma sogs gtsang mas dam kha byed pa las /
NK041(di)006:82: ko spyin gtan nas bsre mi chog /
NK041(di)006:83: dang po gnas ri gang du gcod skabs nas shar
NK041(di)006:84: rtags ma nor bar bzhag pa de rten gyi mdun
NK041(di)006:86: mdun ngos kyi gnas lngar 'ja' gur re'i khungs su /
NK041(di)006:88: zhes lany+dzanara 'bur ma brko yang legs /
NK041(di)006:90: rnam rgyal mchod rten yod na bum sgor b+h+r+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)006:91: a mrita a yurda de s+w+aa h+aa bri /
NK041(di)006:92: mi shong na rnam rgyal mchod rten gyi rtsa bar bri /
NK041(di)006:93: mchod rten med na rtse klad du nyal stabs su bri steng /
NK041(di)006:95: dbu dang bre'i thad tsam du sarba bid+y+aa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)006:97: snying dang bum dbus tsam du /
NK041(di)006:101: bri ste sum 'bud byed kyang legs te /
NK041(di)006:102: de gsum ka'ang sku khang lta bu'i 'ja' gur nya mgo can gyi nang du bri /
NK041(di)006:103: srog shing chen po la rgyas par bris mos na /
NK041(di)006:104: rnam rgyal mchod rten gyi nyi ma la a /
NK041(di)006:105: zla ba la 'ahahshahsahmahhah gdugs la mamakolingasaman+tahbri /
NK041(di)006:106: rtsa ba rdo rje phyed pa'i pad 'dab bzhi la
NK041(di)006:107: b+h+r+aum re rwa bzhi la'ang b+h+r+aum re mtshams bzhi'i khongs
NK041(di)006:108: su 'ja' skor nya mgo can du gzhi mthing ga
NK041(di)006:111: mgrin pa dang bre mgul gyi thad tsam du dbyangs gsal ngos re la tshar re bri /
NK041(di)006:112: snying khar +aa yu she'i 'og nas ngos so sor
NK041(di)006:113: gzungs chen sde lnga spar ma ltar rgyas pa bri
NK041(di)006:114: / ma shong na gzungs thung bri ste /
NK041(di)006:115: shar du gtsug tor rnam rgyal ni /
NK041(di)006:119: zhes tshar du shong gi mjug tu /
NK041(di)006:120: ye d+har tshar ci shong dang yed+hara gyi bod skad
NK041(di)006:121: ni chos rnams thams cad rgyu las sogs kyang bri
NK041(di)006:122: / de mthar rabs bdun gso sbyong rgyas pa ni /
NK041(di)006:123: zin bris gzhan phan zla snang na bzhugs pa ltar bri bod skad tsam ni sor mdo na'ang snang /
NK041(di)006:124: bsdu na rnam gzigs gso sbyong ni k+sh+aan+tihparamitatapad+d+hah nahiprabradzitah paroparot+aap+aish+ramanah zhes pa bod skad du /
NK041(di)006:125: bzod pa dka' thub dam pa bzod pa ni /
NK041(di)006:126: mya ngan 'das pa mchog ces sangs rgyas gsungs /
NK041(di)006:127: rab tu byung ba bzhan la gnod pa dang /
NK041(di)006:128: gzhan la 'tshe ba dge sbyong ma yin no //
NK041(di)006:130: nyin mo bde legs nyin mo bde legs mtshan bde legs //
NK041(di)006:131: nyi ma'i gung yang bde legs shing //
NK041(di)006:132: nyin mtshan rtag tu bde legs pa //
NK041(di)006:133: dkon mchog gsum gyi bkra shis shog /
NK041(di)006:134: bsod nams ri bo bsod nams ri bo bzhin du brtan pa dang //
NK041(di)006:135: brgyud 'dzin nyi zla bzhin du gsal ba dang //
NK041(di)006:136: snyan grags nam mkha' lta bur khyab gyur pa'i //
NK041(di)006:137: gsum po des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)006:138: lo brgya thub cing lo brgya thub cing ston brgya mthong ba dang //
NK041(di)006:139: tshe ring nad med bde skyid phun sum tshogs //
NK041(di)006:140: theg pa mchog la nges par 'byung ba ste //
NK041(di)006:141: lnga po des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)006:142: bstan pa'i dpal gyur bla med zhabs pad brtan //
NK041(di)006:143: bstan 'dzin skyes bus sa steng yongs la khyab //
NK041(di)006:144: bstan pa'i sbyin bdag mnga' thang 'byor pa rgyas //
NK041(di)006:145: bstan pa yun ring gnas pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK041(di)006:146: lta bu'i bkra shis gang 'os re bri /
NK041(di)006:151: samb+haramama+aayuh samshod+haya 'di gzungs spar rnams na med kyang /
NK041(di)006:152: gzungs mdo dngos na bzhugs pas chad pa 'dra /
NK041(di)006:158: bkra shis bcas sngar ltar bri //
NK041(di)006:159: nub tu gsang ba ring bsrel /
NK041(di)006:162: ci shong mthar sngar ltar sbyar /
NK041(di)006:167: ci shong dang rten snying gso sbyong rgya skad bod skad gang mos /
NK041(di)006:168: bkra shis bcas lhag chad bris sub med par bri'o //
NK041(di)006:169: mchod rten srog shing la gzab /
NK041(di)006:170: ces pa yin pas srog shing las skabs thams cad
NK041(di)006:171: du gso sbyong blang nas gtsang sbra la gnas te
NK041(di)006:172: kha shubs dang lag lcibs gon /
NK041(di)006:173: sbyong khrus dang gzungs sgrub tshar nas gzungs 'bul tshe smra ba bcad la /
NK041(di)006:174: man+t+ra d+h+aa tu gar+b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)006:181: sdig pa ci yang bzod pa dka' thub bkra shis
NK041(di)006:182: bcas 'don bzhin du phul bar rnams gur gum spos
NK041(di)006:183: phyes gtams / gzungs 'gar rig pa phug ron ni /
NK041(di)006:188: tshar nas kyang sbyang khrus rab gnas phral du bya /
NK041(di)006:189: yang khung bu mi 'ju ba'i srog shing phra mo
NK041(di)006:190: la phyi nas gzungs dril phyogs phyogs su bcings kyang
NK041(di)006:191: chog / gzungs phul lugs 'di mchod rten cha brgyad
NK041(di)006:192: khang brtsegs sogs gyi rigs thams cad spyi 'gres yin
NK041(di)006:193: chog / / lha la srog shing gtso bar ma
NK041(di)006:194: bshad pas gzungs mdo'i glegs bam dang gzungs 99re dgos
NK041(di)006:195: pa rnams ci bde byas kyang chad skyon med de
NK041(di)006:196: lha rang rang gi srog sngags sogs dmigs bsal gtso
NK041(di)006:197: chog / / bo byed dgos / chos skyong gi
NK041(di)006:198: rigs la drag po'i shing gi srog shing sogs skabs
NK041(di)006:199: chog / / bo byed dgos / thob dpyad /
NK041(di)006:200: gzungs dang srog shing gi na bza' rnams kyang zhi
NK041(di)006:201: rgyas dbang drag gang yin gyi rang mdog chog ste
NK041(di)006:202: chog / / bo byed dgos / thob dpyad /
NK041(di)006:203: / yongs grags ser po yin rtsa ba'i rdo rje
NK041(di)006:204: rwa bar rnams su rin chen phye ma thum po
NK041(di)006:205: chog / / bo byed dgos / thob dpyad /
NK041(di)006:206: / bcer la / 'aphanga lo la de'i gzungs 99dkri
NK041(di)006:207: chog / / bo byed dgos / thob dpyad /
NK041(di)006:208: / bcer la / / srog shing gi h+aum thad
NK041(di)006:209: du gzungs chen sde lnga ci mang bcings /
NK041(di)006:211: shin tu mang po 'byor na bum pa'i stod smad bar gsum khengs par gtam /
NK041(di)006:212: lha'i h+aum thad du sde lnga nyung tsam dang lha
NK041(di)006:213: rang rang gi bsnyen sngags kho nas khengs par bya
NK041(di)006:214: / rten chung ngu sogs kyi srog shing la gnas yig 'bru lnga dang /
NK041(di)006:215: sarba bid+y+aa a yu she su pra tish+tha ye d+har tsam bris kyang 'thus /
NK041(di)006:219: shin tu chung ngu la &a+aah&amh'u &abrisa kyang chog gsungs /
NK041(di)006:220: nang gzhug gzhan rnams mtho dman go rim ni yig
NK041(di)006:221: cha rnams nas kyang go rim mi 'dra ba cung
NK041(di)006:222: zad re snang yang spyi rgyug tsam ni /
NK041(di)006:223: s+aats+tsha rnams bum pa'i nang gzhugs /
NK041(di)006:224: ma shong na rmang dge yan chad bzhugs kyang rung /
NK041(di)006:225: bum gter rnams dang sa 'dzin skor la gzhug /
NK041(di)006:226: gnod sbyin 'khor lo dang chos skyong skor bsngo smon dang bkra shis skor /
NK041(di)006:227: go cha sogs seng khri'i stod gdong chen thad dang /
NK041(di)006:229: tshad med dang skyil krung nang du tsasher tshaphyin dzamdo sde skor /
NK041(di)006:230: bum gdan dang gsang ba skor bala mabya rgyud /
NK041(di)006:232: bum smad dang lte bar parnal 'byor rgyud /
NK041(di)006:234: bum dbus dang mthar phaskor la rang rang gi sgrub sngags dang /
NK041(di)006:235: jama nyah+aa tayo thaga'i daskor na dgongs 'dus mthong grol /
NK041(di)006:237: bum stod dang sku stod la /
NK041(di)006:238: a nu yo ga dang a ti yo ga cabla sgrub zhi drag /
NK041(di)006:243: sangs rgyas byang sems kyi mtshan /
NK041(di)006:245: bre dang dbu la rim par kabla ma khabrgyud gapa'i ngamtshan sngags /
NK041(di)006:246: snying thig gi btags grol chargyud drug 'di rnams tshe
NK041(di)006:247: gshis dang a 'dzam sgar spar glegs bam sor bzhi
NK041(di)006:248: pa bzhugs / sangs rgyas sras gcig /
NK041(di)006:250: srog shing gi rtser rnam rgyal bum nang dang lha'i
NK041(di)006:251: gtsug tor du yungs 'bru lta bu'i ring bsrel dar
NK041(di)006:252: gyi bstum ste rin po che'i ga 'ur stsal ba
NK041(di)006:253: bzhugs su gsol / tshul 'di ni rnying lugs yin /
NK041(di)006:254: gsar lugs la nang rgyud sde gsum mal du /
NK041(di)006:255: pha ma gnyis med rgyud gsum yar spar /
NK041(di)006:256: gzhan yang stod smad thams cad du gzhug chog pa ni /
NK041(di)006:262: yang byang chub shing sogs sangs rgyas dang 'brel ba'i rten rnams dbu la gzhug /
NK041(di)006:263: bla ma mchog gi dbu zhwa sogs sku stod las byung ba rnams stod du gzhug /
NK041(di)006:264: sham thabs sogs sku rmad las byung ba rnams smad du gzhug /
NK041(di)006:265: chos 'khor dang rgyal mtshan nang du gdugs dkar 'khor lo dang rgyal mtshan rtse mo /
NK041(di)006:267: dbu'i gtsug tor du gdugs dkar 'khor lo gzhug /
NK041(di)006:268: bum nang du dri med rnam gnyis kyis dkyil 'khor
NK041(di)006:269: bzhengs skabs sogs rten gyi srog shing ring thung mtha'
NK041(di)006:271: srog shing gi gzungs skor tsam ma gtogs /
NK041(di)006:272: gzungs dang byin rten gzhan mang chen rnams gong ltar rten gyi phyi khog la gzhal te gzhug dgos /
NK041(di)006:273: skye mched byin rlabs so sor sbyar /
NK041(di)006:274: dkyil 'khor med skabs ru shing ngam tshugs shing la srog shing bcing ba yin /
NK041(di)006:275: gzungs 'phred gzhug dgos skabs byung na /
NK041(di)006:276: dbu g.yas phyogs dang rgyab phyogs gang bder bstan /
NK041(di)006:277: glegs bam rigs kyang dbu rgyab phyogs su bstan la dbu ldeb yar bstan gsungs /
NK041(di)006:278: spyir rten bzhengs 'phro lus pa la bar chad mi
NK041(di)006:279: 'jug pa'i phyir gu gul bdug bzo bo'i lag cha
NK041(di)006:280: bzhag / gos dmar ser gyis bkab /
NK041(di)006:281: steng nas byin ldan gyis mnan gsungs /
NK041(di)006:282: srog shing sogs snga tshags dgos pas rnams nyer mkho dgos pa kun tshang ltar thugs 'jags /
NK041(di)006:284: mchod rten che chung gang yin na'ang dri med rnam
NK041(di)006:285: gnyis kyi cho gas bsgrubs pa zhig byung na sa
NK041(di)006:286: rdo las bcos kyang 'brel tshad don ldan byas pa
NK041(di)006:288: de ltar ma yin gser dngul las bcos pa'ang rten phal pa tsam las mi 'gyur /
NK041(di)006:290: 'jam dpal bde ba'i nyi ma'i sku gdung lta bu la /
NK041(di)006:291: rtsa gsum gzungs 'jug spyi ltar las /
NK041(di)006:293: bum dbus su lhag pa'i lha 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi gser sku'am 'dag sku gzungs gzhug byin ldan /
NK041(di)006:294: de'i thugs kar phyi nang gang bder shel rdo h+aum gis mtshan pa /
NK041(di)006:297: mtshungs med chos rje 'jam dpal bde ba'i nyi ma
NK041(di)006:298: dpal bzang po zhes bgyi ba'i thugs kyi dgongs pa
NK041(di)006:299: zab mo gong nas gong du yongs su rdzogs par
NK041(di)006:300: gyur cig / 'brel thogs bdag cag rnams kyang tshe rabs kun tu rjes su gzung bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)006:301: rjes 'jug bstan pa'i mnga' thang yun ring du rgyas par gyur cig /
NK041(di)006:302: ces pa lta bu'i 'dod gsol gyis dril spro na gter mdzod nipar sku gdung mchod tshul nang ni /
NK041(di)006:304: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sogs tshang ba phreng gcig tu bri nus na shin tu legs /
NK041(di)006:305: de dang mnyam du gdung gi s+aats+tsha /
NK041(di)006:306: bla ma'i thugs dam gyi rten gang rnyed /
NK041(di)006:307: 'jam dpal gyi chos glegs bam rigs dang a ra
NK041(di)006:308: pa tsa sogs bsnyen pa shin tu mang po gzhug
NK041(di)006:309: / sgrub tshe dri med rnam gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor mchod rten nang du rgyun bzhag ma shong na'ang /
NK041(di)006:310: phyi rol dkyil 'khor bshams nas bsgrub la srog shing phul /
NK041(di)006:311: rjes dkyil 'khor mi mngon par bsdu bar gsungs so //
NK041(di)006:312: rabs gnas skabs su thugs dam gang yin gyi sgrub pa des khog phub na legs snyam mo //
NK041(di)006:313: yang sngar ma grags kyang rang bzo byas na /
NK041(di)006:314: phyi rol sa rdo las byang chub mchod rten chung
NK041(di)006:315: 'bring bzhengs skabs bum nang du dkyil 'khor sgrub stabs
NK041(di)006:317: snga mo nas shing gi sgam bang sgrom gsum brtsegs bzos nas /
NK041(di)006:319: lha khang lta bur bkod nas mchod rdzas rgyan bcas tshang bar bshams /
NK041(di)006:320: de'ang rnam lnga sogs ni 'og gzhi la gro skyo sman 'dam gyis sbyar /
NK041(di)006:321: 'phan gdugs rnams ni bla re la dpyangs te mi
NK041(di)006:322: 'gyel ba'i thabs barlinga bar byas nas steng ma'i bla
NK041(di)006:323: re dang spang leb la srog shing shong nges pa'i
NK041(di)006:325: dkyil 'khor gnyis tshul bzhin bsgrubs nas 'jog /
NK041(di)006:326: nam phyi rol gyi mchod rten bum pa'i phyed bar brtsigs zin pa dang /
NK041(di)006:327: bum gdan yan chad tshugs shing med par byas te /
NK041(di)006:328: dkyil 'khor gnyis po dal bus spyan drangs nas bzhag
NK041(di)006:329: la mchod rdzas 'gyel ba dang phos pa byung na
NK041(di)006:330: legs par bcos / ser sbreng pa rnams nas sems
NK041(di)006:331: can shes bcu sogs 'don gyin srog shig 'dzugs te
NK041(di)006:332: sgom gsum pa brtsegs pa'i nang du s+aats+tsha bzhag pas
NK041(di)006:333: srog shing skyor te mi 'khyor ba bya zhing /
NK041(di)006:334: s+aats+tshasa bum pa bkang ste rtsig 'phro nyi zla'i bar mthar phyin par bya /
NK041(di)006:335: rab gnas bsdus pas bdag la /
NK041(di)006:336: zhal ba lan grangs tshon rtsi bcas 'jog mtshams grub pa'i tshe /
NK041(di)006:337: slar srog shing 'dzugs chog gshar rgyug ma zhig btang ba'i sgrub mchod tshar ba dang /
NK041(di)006:338: phyi rol mchod bshams rgyas pa bya ba nas rjes chog mthar phyin par bya /
NK041(di)006:339: phyi nyin rab gnas rgyas pa bya ba na 'jug pa bde ste /
NK041(di)006:340: dper na gnod sbyin 'khor lo dang bum gter sngar
NK041(di)006:341: nas sgrub pa bzhin du nyes 'gal med snyam lags
NK041(di)006:342: / sngar yig cha'i steng nas zhus shing mkhyen bzhin
NK041(di)006:343: pa gzhir bzhag nas re zhig brjed tho de tsam
